trans-unit.source: Defines a set of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref> fields that each correspond to a command function provided by the host environment.
trans-unit.target: 집합을 정의 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"> </xref> 각 호스트 환경에서 제공 하는 명령 함수에 해당 하는 필드입니다.

trans-unit.source: MenuCommands contains a set of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> fields that can be used to specify a command to link when adding a command using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.
trans-unit.target: MenuCommands는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> 메서드</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> 를 사용 하 여 명령을 추가할 때 연결할 명령을 지정 하려면 사용할 수 있는 필드</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> 의 집합을 포함
